title: Nebius AI + Helicone
description: Introducing the integration of Nebius AI with Helicone's observability platform. This integration enables comprehensive monitoring and analytics for Nebius's powerful image generation models, including Flux and Stability AI's SDXL. Leverage Helicone's advanced observability features to track costs, monitor performance, and optimize your Nebius AI implementations while maintaining full visibility into your model interactions and usage patterns.
